@startuml
title 图像处理任务 - 状态图

state "Created\n已创建" as Created
state "Queued\n等待执行" as Queued
state "Running\n后台执行" as Running
state "Cancelling\n请求取消" as Cancelling
state "Completed\n已完成" as Completed
state "Failed\n失败" as Failed
state "Canceled\n已取消" as Canceled

[*] --> Created
Created --> Queued: submit
Queued --> Running: worker available
Running --> Running: report progress
Running --> Completed: result produced
Running --> Failed: processing error
Running --> Cancelling: cancel requested
Queued --> Canceled: cancel before start
Cancelling --> Canceled: cleanup done
Failed --> Queued: retry
Completed --> [*]
Failed --> [*]
Canceled --> [*]

note right of Running
  用于拼接、EDF 等耗时处理。
  UI 只接收进度和完成通知，
  不直接执行大图计算。
end note

@enduml
